data.description: Look no further, this is home! Seller willing to assist with closing cost or mortgage rate buy down.  This beautiful, well-maintained, 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath, Georgian style brick home boasts the pride of the neighborhood as it has unique tuckpointing features nestled away on a cul-de-sac street with long-time residents as neighbors. This home makes city living available with a suburban feel. The home features hardwood floors and custom doors; the staircase leads up to 3 spacious bedrooms and a full bath, a basement that can easily accommodate an additional bedroom, bath, theater room, gym, etc.; there is an additional room with patio doors leading to the backyard that can serve as an office or family room. The home offers a formal living room with a real wood-burning fireplace and a formal dining room. The kitchen includes granite countertops, light grey cabinets, and stainless steel appliances; the wooded fenced makes the backyard a private oasis with seasonal annual flowers, greenery, and a beautiful red tree perfect for relaxing or entertaining.  Nothing left to do but move in and make it home. Schedule your viewing today.
